<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Next Frontier Financial Services | Premium Bookkeeping & Tax Strategy</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Meticulous bookkeeping and proactive tax execution designed for business owners seeking financial clarity and room to scale.">
    
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Next Frontier Financial Services | Bookkeeping & Tax Strategy">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Bringing pristine clarity and intentional financial stability to your business journey.">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght=300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght=0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* Modern CSS Reset & Core Brand Variables */
        :root {
            --charcoal: #232B2B;
            --sage-dark: #4A5D4E;
            --sage: #7A9A82;
            --sage-light: #EBF0EC;
            --sand-light: #F9F8F6;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --text-main: #2D312E;
            --text-muted: #5A605B;
            --font-serif: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            --font-sans: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            color: var(--text-main);
            background-color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        /* Navigation Style */
        header {
            background-color: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 1rem 0; 
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .logo-img {
            width: 50px;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .logo-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .brand-main {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .brand-sub {
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-left: 2rem;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--sage);
        }

        .nav-btn {
            background-color: var(--charcoal);
            color: var(--white) !important;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--sage-dark);
        }

        /* Split Hero Layout */
        .hero-split {
            background-color: var(--sand-light);
            padding: 8rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.05);
        }

        .hero-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--charcoal);
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--sage-dark);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid var(--charcoal);
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: var(--charcoal);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .hero-showcase {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.12);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(35, 43, 43, 0.04);
        }

        .hero-showcase h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .trust-list {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .trust-list li {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-weight: 500;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .trust-list li span {
            color: var(--sage-dark);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Section Global Settings */
        .section-padding {
            padding: 7rem 0;
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 5rem auto;
        }

        .section-header span {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--sage-dark);
            font-weight: 600;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        /* Process Section with Mountain Background */
        .process-section {
            position: relative;
            background-color: var(--charcoal);
            background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(35, 43, 43, 0.7), rgba(42, 53, 46, 0.8)), 
                              url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .process-section .section-header span { color: var(--sage); }
        .process-section .section-header h2 { color: var(--white); }

        .process-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .process-card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98); 
            padding: 3.5rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-align: left;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .process-icon {
            width: 45px;
            height: 45px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: var(--sage-light);
            color: var(--sage-dark);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .process-card h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* About Section Styles */
        .about-section {
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
            gap: 5rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-image-container {
            position: relative;
        }

        .about-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            max-height: 520px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .about-image-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: -20px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--sage);
            border-radius: 4px;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .about-content span {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--sage-dark);
            font-weight: 600;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .about-content h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.25;
        }

        .about-content p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .about-highlights {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .highlight-item {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* Directional Focus Navigation Grid */
        .focus-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .focus-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.12);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 4rem 3rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .focus-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(35,43,43,0.05);
            border-color: var(--sage);
        }

        .focus-card h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .focus-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-focus {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--charcoal);
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-focus:hover {
            background-color: var(--sage-dark);
        }

        /* Brand Color Rotation Injections */
        .why-choose-us-section {
            background-color: var(--charcoal);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .why-choose-us-section .section-header span {
            color: var(--sage);
        }

        .why-choose-us-section .section-header h2 {
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .why-choose-us-section .focus-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr) !important; 
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .why-choose-us-section .focus-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            padding: 4rem 3rem; 
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
        }

        /* Who We Serve Redesign Styles */
        .who-we-serve-section {
            background: var(--sage-light);
        }

        .support-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .support-card {
            background: var(--charcoal);
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
            transition: .25s;
        }

        .support-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: var(--sage-dark);
        }

        .support-card-icon {
            color: var(--sage);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .support-card-icon svg {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        .support-card h3 {
            color: var(--white);
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .support-card p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .82);
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
        }

        /* FAQ Accordion Styling Mechanics */
        .faq-section {
            background-color: var(--sand-light);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.1);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.1);
        }

        .faq-container {
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .faq-item {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.12);
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(35, 43, 43, 0.01);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .faq-trigger {
            width: 100%;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: left;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--charcoal);
        }

        .faq-trigger:hover {
            background-color: rgba(122, 154, 130, 0.04);
        }

        .faq-icon {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--sage-dark);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-block;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .faq-content {
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.3s cubic-bezier(0, 1, 0, 1);
        }

        .faq-content p {
            padding: 0 2rem 1.5rem 2rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            line-height: 1.65;
        }

        /* Active State Architecture via JS Toggle */
        .faq-item.is-active {
            border-color: var(--sage);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.04);
        }

        .faq-item.is-active .faq-content {
            max-height: 500px; 
            transition: max-height 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .faq-item.is-active .faq-icon {
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            color: var(--sage);
        }

        /* Inline Cal.com Embed Environment - Soft Light Sage Background */
        .booking-section {
            padding: 7rem 0;
            background-color:var(--sage-light); /* Kept as light sage for balanced aesthetic layout */
        }

        .booking-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        .booking-intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 3.5rem auto;
        }

        .booking-tag {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--sage-dark);
            font-weight: 600;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .booking-intro h2 {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .booking-intro p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .scheduler-frame-wrapper {
            background-color: var(--white); /* White card frame to let widget interface blend cleanly */
            border: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.12);
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(35, 43, 43, 0.06);
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 700px; 
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Engagement Banner */
        .cta-banner {
            background-color: var(--charcoal);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 6rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta-banner h2 {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .btn-banner-action {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--sage);
            color: var(--charcoal);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-banner-action:hover {
            background-color: var(--sage-light);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--sand-light);
            padding: 4rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.1);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .footer-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--sage-dark);
        }

        /* Responsive Breakpoints */
        @media(max-width:992px){
            .support-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
            .why-choose-us-section .focus-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 1100px) {
            .why-choose-us-section .focus-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }

        @media(max-width:768px){
            .support-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 650px) {
            .why-choose-us-section .focus-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .faq-trigger {
                padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .faq-content p {
                padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem 1.5rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; text-align: center; }
            .hero-buttons { justify-content: center; }
            .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
            .about-image-container { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-content h1 { font-size: 2.6rem; }
            .section-header h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .nav-wrapper { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
            .nav-links { margin-top: 1rem; }
            nav a { margin: 0 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
            .nav-btn { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

{% include "layouts/header.njk" %}

    <!-- Split Hero Section (Sand Light) -->
    <section class="hero-split">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-grid">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <p class="eyebrow" style="font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--sage-dark); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; text-transform: uppercase;">
                        Bookkeeping • Tax Preparation • Tax Planning
                    </p>
                    <h1>Clean Books.<br>Clear Taxes.<br>Confident Growth.</h1>
                    <p>You didn’t start your business to manage spreadsheets or worry about tax deadlines. We handle your bookkeeping, tax preparation, and year-round planning so you always know exactly where your business stands—and what to do next.</p>
                    <div class="hero-buttons">
                        <a href="#onboarding-frontier" class="btn-primary">Schedule your free Strategy Call</a>
                        <a href="#focus-selection" class="btn-secondary">Explore Our Services</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-showcase">
                    <h3>Our Commitments</h3>
                    <ul class="trust-list">
                        <li><span>✓</span> Monthly Bookkeeping Packages</li>
                        <li><span>✓</span> Tax Preparation and Planning</li>
                        <li><span>✓</span> Secure Cloud Accounting</li>
                        <li><span>✓</span> Personalized Support</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Workflow Section (Charcoal Overlay Background) -->
    <section class="section-padding process-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span>How It Works</span>
                <h2>Simple Financial Support For Your Business</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="process-grid">
                <div class="process-card">
                    <div class="process-icon">1</div>
                    <h3>Book your Consultation</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem;">We'll learn about your business, your goals, and your current bookkeeping or tax challenges.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="process-card">
                    <div class="process-icon">2</div>
                    <h3>We organize your Finances</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem;">We keep your books accurate, organized, and tax-ready throughout the year so you always know where your business stands.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="process-card">
                    <div class="process-icon">3</div>
                    <h3>Grow with Confidence</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem;">With reliable financial reports and proactive tax planning, you can make better business decisions while we handle the numbers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Editorial Identity Component (White Background) -->
    <section class="section-padding about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-image-container">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Next Frontier Financial Services Corporate Workspace" class="about-image">
                </div>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <span>Your Financial Partner</span>
                    <h3>Built for Business Owners Who Want to Stay Ahead of Taxes, Not Chase Them</h3>
                    <p>Most business owners don’t struggle because they’re unorganized—they struggle because they don’t have clear financial visibility. We fix that by keeping your books clean, your taxes planned, and your financial decisions informed.</p>
